Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----SUB----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.24,0:00:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.02,0:00:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.65,0:00:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼到了 這種地方來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次休假有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼問
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 班上的同學邀請我一起去去海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 想找郁乃也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海邊嗎 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.92,0:01:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 好不容易才好起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老姐你班上的人我又不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不過 河野同學你不是認識的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.37,0:01:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河野
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是姐姐的男朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男 男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 而且 提出待郁乃一起去的是河野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.13,0:01:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.11,0:01:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河野同學很溫柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 去也不是不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 那麼 去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後還是來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來玩如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.44,0:01:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 黏得來一次海邊的說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼熱的天氣 找人出來完的人是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 我也不是來玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 為啥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是老姐的保護人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~ 好懶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去水邊看看嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 難得來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 飲料 很清涼的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這裡還有唷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 還有些冰鎮的點心哦 要吃嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我那麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我稍微去玩一一下囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 您走好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛 我都說了會痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還是覺得那傢伙不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯呢 很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是百花繚亂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,環姐姐好厲害~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是環姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 身材很好的前輩麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那個究竟 是們麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 對不起 河野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老~姐~ 你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到海邊究竟是來做啥的? 嗚?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是來狩獵的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 狩獵?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對露來說大海邊就是狩獵的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對嗚來說不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難易度好高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧 嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個 我還有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉體活動的時候 特別是運動的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往體內攝取一定量的果糖 對嗚和露來說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是非常重要的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我 又沒在運動...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露 這樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 露來喝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麼! 嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露子的是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼? 嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喝這個的話 就不會幹什麼正常的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 只有這個不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露好傷心 露~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果雖然好像完全沒搞清楚什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似連那個個小不可思議也擊退了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敗給他了 喝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪種笑法 算什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼難得出來玩一趟 我想還是跟大家一起玩完比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過 我是作為保護人來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天可是有很多奇怪的蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 蟲子是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:09:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 看來小郁乃妹妹還真是喜歡姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就不用找我一起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只約姐姐不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你問我為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為大家一起來不是比較開心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 姐姐這種男人哪裡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 只有阿貴一個人喝飲料 真狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩? 啊 稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,間 間接接吻!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.09,0:09:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好喝～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天然呆? 還是說是故意的?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙怎麼還這麼冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我們正在築沙做城堡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 小郁乃也來嘛~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變主意的話隨時可以來唷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 這這個就是妹妹的角色麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到男生的話 這傢伙也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單看長相的話 這個也還不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹 幹啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.64,0:11:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 真不錯啊 草帽配白色連衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛少女在海潘獨自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌啊 萌啊 了不起 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這傢伙不行 絕對不會受女生歡迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 稍微有點生氣的表情太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 能稍微給我點笑容嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.22,0:11:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁乃妹妹很不起歡你這麼做吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 對不起 所以請破壞那相機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒收!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 小貴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豪不在乎地把便當第一個發給他了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便當啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老姐你該不會什麼都沒帶帶來吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從和野同學那聽說 向版前輩會準備大家的份帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉~ 不是這個問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 快看快看 好像很好吃耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親手做的便當才是這種活動的關鍵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 大家快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅長料理的御姐角色嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好對付啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿貴阿貴 這個好好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我吃這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以 這個我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個可只有一個啊 你還拿?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把這個給我!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擋!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可不行哦 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在為止都還是妹妹的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙怎麼想的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老姐 好好幹啦 男朋友被人搶了也沒關係嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩? 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 想喝點什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這個很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 我邊當裡也有放
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟 是在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個料理 在這顆星球是第四美味的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個星球? 第四?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一天來到露的星球 就把嗚任命為露的廚師長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.79,0:14:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣了 環姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很好 嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 大家都在笑?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 真的很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 喝點這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不盡 感激不盡 真的感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不認真
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:14:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去也沒關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.79,0:15:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 在叫你唷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 郁乃也一起去吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在叫老姐你麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正來到在海邊 郁乃也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我負責看行李
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 一個人沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起 對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 雖然是很符合老姐的做事風格啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有妹系角色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有御姐角色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個不可思議的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 姐姐的情情勢真是很嚴峻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像她這樣種感覺的 沒有什麼特點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 也不明白那傢伙在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我先休息一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個好像在圖鑒上看見過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也不太明白 不過螃蟹也就是螃蟹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個能吃嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼 原來到這裡來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 又是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你來幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找你呢 因為你突然不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不用管頁可以地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個問題 不過邀請人可是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那邊的人拋下 不用管沒有關係嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 反正那邊也有環姐在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.98,0:19:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木實和露子雖然看上去那樣 但是很有精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然雄二有點那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 班長也在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還讓人搞不清楚想法的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆再說麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著在這一帶不放心讓郁乃妹妹落單...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 還真是體貼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁乃妹妹?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~ 原來你們在這裡~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找了好久哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧!    老姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 小牧同學...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 河野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 是海螺 海螺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 小牧同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有海膽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之看起來沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 阿貴好像不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們倆個鑽到什麼地方去親熱了...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄二?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 因為不知到廁所在哪裡所以跑遠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去買果汁了吧? 不要緊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 小牧同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.38,0:20:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說我也是「小牧同學」..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對 確實是這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫郁乃時會叫郁乃妹妹...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:21:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 也 是 「小牧同學」 的 說!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就叫 郁乃妹妹和…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁乃妹妹和…?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁乃妹妹和…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛佳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.79,0:21:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 後面的就留給年輕人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁乃妹妹?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 郁乃~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.46,0:22:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個…不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.37,0:22:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.75,0:22:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 嗯…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海螺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.18,0:22:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海螺?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對 海螺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海螺你個頭啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 姐姐在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.15,0:22:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不ˋ知道在幹什麼的人 我也不是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.19,0:23:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢 要上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.05,0:23:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.24,0:23:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.32,0:23:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴…那個…蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.97,0:23:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴蟹? 噢 螃蟹?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.17,0:23:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.17,0:23:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹個頭啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.43,0:23:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的老姐振作點吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.33,0:24:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁乃妹妹?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.51,0:24:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁乃?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.14,0:24:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.64,0:24:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭到腳了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.96,0:24:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 肩膀借你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.95,0:24:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.59,0:24:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情你對老姐做不就好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.04,0:24:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁乃!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.99,0:24:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊 因為你受傷了我才這樣做的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.08,0:24:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.16,0:24:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.69,0:24:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.63,0:24:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 貴明
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.95,0:24:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.75,0:24:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了 剛剛叫了「貴明」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.39,0:24:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁 郁乃!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.58,0:24:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼不好的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.20,0:24:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.92,0:24:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴明?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.76,0:24:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的! 郁乃~
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.62,0:25:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就ok了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.50,0:25:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.46,0:25:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.99,0:25:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得蠻漂亮的嘛 你這個有愛的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.06,0:25:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.21,0:25:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 還裝傻…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.56,0:25:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.81,0:25:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.59,0:25:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 痛 很痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.98,0:25:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了 很痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.64,0:25:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個硬梆梆的傢伙 是嗚的食物妈?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.14,0:25:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.52,0:25:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.06,0:25:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廚師長 這個要怎麼吃?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.00,0:25:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 是~我~的~啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.94,0:25:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.37,0:25:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.62,0:26:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}好燙好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.52,0:26:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是 也要去買套泳裝呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.85,0:26:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 然後再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.49,0:26:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要在抓些海螺才行
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.41,0:26:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.69,0:26:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 老姐不加油也不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.62,0:26:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同學和郁乃妹妹都過來吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.15,0:26:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你男朋友貴明在叫你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.47,0:26:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.69,0:26:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁乃?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.14,0:26:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定能實現的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.63,0:26:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 夏天也才剛開始嘛 不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.42,0:28:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露～
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.74,0:28:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22\fad(800,800)}高實用性! 露語講座
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.24,0:28:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露～
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.89,0:28:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了這次的實用性很高的露語講座時間
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.65,0:28:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,講解人是我 草壁優季和
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.51,0:28:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屜森花梨
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.70,0:28:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有大家所熟悉的露子·美麗的天空小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.50,0:28:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露～
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.64,0:28:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.10,0:28:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.16,0:28:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼上一回我們學習了舉辦喜事和喪事時的露語
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.01,0:29:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-1}今天是面向日常生活 我們來學習各種場合下的的露語吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.97,0:29:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們就進入模擬回放場景吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.44,0:29:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露～
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.92,0:29:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水桶打翻 連衣服裏面都濕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.64,0:29:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候應該
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.18,0:29:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露～露露～ 露～露露～
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.88,0:29:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能和雙胞胎一起做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.02,0:29:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候應該
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.40,0:29:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露～露露～ 露～露露～
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.14,0:29:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰到了至今未遇的強敵 內心興奮不已
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.79,0:29:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候應該
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.24,0:29:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露～露露～ 露～露露～
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.70,0:29:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫狐貍的時候應該
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.17,0:29:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露～露～露～
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.84,0:29:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-1}如何 這樣就對日常生活中形形色色的露語有所瞭解了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.58,0:29:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一回大家就來學習一下被蠻橫的前學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.60,0:29:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擾亂學園祭時經常用到的露語
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.20,0:29:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家一起來 露～
